                <h1>USPS Job Disqualifications: Key Factors to Consider</h1>
                <p>USPS disqualifications can arise from various factors, including criminal records, failure to meet specific employment eligibility criteria, or lacking the necessary physical fitness. Applicants must also adhere to ethical standards; any dishonesty during the hiring process may lead to immediate disqualification. Understanding these factors is crucial for prospective candidates.</p>
